 ans et sa mère, Judith Orabilis, avait 18 ans. Il a épousé Matilda de Senlis environ 1136. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils et 1 fille. Il est décédé environ 1158, à Winchester, Hampshire, Angleterre, à l’âge de 69 ans, et a été enterré à Winchester, Hampshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1090–about 1158":"1090–um 1158","1090–1158":"1090–1158","1092–Female":"1092–Verstorben","1090–1163":"1090–1163","1138–1190":"1138–1190","1140–1197":"1140–1197","1140–1204":"1140–1204","1066–1098":"1066–1098","1073–Female":"1073–Verstorben","1190":"1190","1090":"1090","about 1140":"um 1140","1066":"1066","1098":"1098","1197":"1197","1163":"1163","1096":"1096","1140":"1140","1073":"1073","1092":"1092","1106":"1106","1138":"1138","1204":"1204","1158":"1158","about 1136":"um 1136","about 1158":"um 1158","Leicestershire, England":"Leicestershire, England","Winchester, Hampshire, England":"Winchester, Hampshire, England, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Scotland","Daventry, Northamptonshire, England":"Daventry, Northamptonshire, England","Long Buckby, Northamptonshire, England":"Long Buckby, Northamptonshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als Lord Saher de Quincy 1090 in Daventry, Northamptonshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Richard de Quincy 24 und seine Mutter Judith Orabilis 18. Er hat um 1136 Matilda de Senlis geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne und 1 Tochter. Er starb um 1158 im Alter von 69 Jahren in Winchester, Hampshire, England und wurde in Winchester, Hampshire, England, United Kingdom begraben."},"ht":{"1090–about 1158":"1090–about 1158","1090–1158":"1090–1158","1092–Female":"1092–Desede","1090–1163":"1090–1163","1138–1190":"1138–1190","1140–1197":"1140–1197","1140–1204":"1140–1204","1066–1098":"1066–1098","1073–Female":"1073–Desede","1190":"1190","1090":"1090","about 1140":"about 1140","1066":"1066","1098":"1098","1197":"1197","1163":"1163","1096":"1096","1140":"1140","1073":"1073","1092":"1092","1106":"1106","1138":"1138","1204":"1204","1158":"1158","about 1136":"abou